name: Hachikō (Injective)
description: The start of INJECTIVE’s run begins with Hachiko $HACHI will be the biggest token on INJ, the dog 9 years in the making. After waiting 9 years for his Owner Hachiko returned home to find a USB drive in the safe.. This wasn’t your run-of-the-mill code – it was a key to a chaotic digital realm. Instead of keeping it low-key, Hachiko went full degen. He discovered the key’s power and decided to disrupt the financial scene. Forget suits and ties; Hachiko wanted decentralized chaos. After years of coding binges, energy drinks, and questionable decisions, Hachiko birthed $HACHI right on the perfect landscape to fuel it, Injective.
